heisigStory: At last we come to the general character meaning stamp. Its elements: staples . . . stamp.
koohiiStory1: Before sticky backs, they had to staple stamps to letters.
koohiiStory2: Aaaagh, this old stamp doesn´t stick! Okay I´ll just staple it.
